column7: Do you use social media applications?
column8: What social media platforms do you use?
column9: What app do you use the most?
column10: How many hours do you spend on social media platforms daily?
column11: Do you feel anxious or stressed after reading negative comments on your posts?
column12: Are you worried about missing out on important information or events when you're not using social media?
column13: Do you feel that using social media has affected your ability to focus and accomplish daily tasks?
column14: Do you think that consuming quick content (such as watching short videos and push notifications...) has affected your patience and ability to deal with long tasks?
column15: Do you use social media right before going to sleep?
column16: Do you have difficulty sleeping because of thinking about what you saw on social media platforms?
column17: Does the number of likes or comments you get on your posts affect you?
column18: Have you changed your opinion or feeling based on the reactions of others on social media platforms?
column19: Do you prefer interacting with friends or family online rather than face-to-face?
column20: How often do you find yourself using social media for longer than you planned?
